					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2063151#post-2732806</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2063151/scp-2492#post-2732806</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 24 Jan 2017 14:14:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Penton</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1998745</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Yes. The idea i had was that the lamp is a sort of beacon which the mother could somehow see from the 'other side'. The mother can reach into the living world but no entirely.</p> <p>As for the injuries getting worse over time, the idea is that the injuries caused from the accident begin to re-manifest and get worse every time -1 reappears. Not to keen on this idea though.</p> </div> </div> </div> <br /> Also, sorry about getting back to you so late.
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
